DOC.detailed_description: This single-center , randomize , open-label , 2-period , 2-sequence , 2-treatment , crossover study healthy men woman compare pharmacokinetics ( PK ) safety profile two 50-mg subcutaneous ( SC ) injection etanercept liquid ( 1.0-mL prefilled syringe ) : ( 1 ) use disposable auto-injector device , ( 2 ) use standard manual injection . Each subject receive injection abdomen , separate washout period 28 day .
